{"id":4911,"created":1449242853,"modified":1449242853,"data":{"arcane_focus_component":"0","area":"","casting_time":"1 standard action","corrupt_component":"0","description_html":"\u003cp\u003eAs \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/status--2517/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003estatus\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, but you can also cast a limited selection of spells through the link, as if you were touching the target. You can cast any spell that meets the following conditions:\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eLevel: 0, 1st, or 2nd\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eRange: Touch\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eTarget: Creature touched\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cli\u003eSaving Throw: Yes (harmless)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor example, if you become aware (through the \u003cem\u003egreater status\u003c/em\u003e spell) that one of your linked companions is dying, you can cast \u003ca href=\"/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/cure-moderate-wounds--2383/\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ecure moderate wounds\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e to try to revive her.\u003c/p\u003e","descriptors":"","divine_focus_component":"1","duration":"1 hour/level","effect":"","id":4911,"material_component":"0","meta_breath_component":"0","name":"Status, Greater","page":116,"rulebook":"Eberron Campaign Setting","saving_throw":"Will negates (harmless)","school":"Divination","somatic_component":"1","spell_range":"Touch","spell_resistance":"Yes (harmless)","subschool":"","target":"One touched creature/3 levels","true_name_component":"0","verbal_component":"1","xp_component":"0"}}